{"tid":128193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"胃裡都是打火機、塑膠玩具　20萬信天翁橫屍中途島","createTime":"2017-02-20T15:18:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-21T01:48:50.000Z","uid":77012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"67e94eb9a49dbfc086beabff8a440e6202fa0a13","tid":128193,"uid":77012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T15:18:25.000Z","msg":"曾經聽聞過一句說話︰「人類是地球的癌細胞。」這句話或許太偏激，卻至少道出了一部份事實。如果你曾經隨手掉過膠水樽到海裏，有想過它最終會飄到甚麼地方嗎？大海雖浩大，卻依然溶解不了一個膠水蓋。美國攝影師 Chris Jordan 前往為於太平洋的 Midway (中途島)，此處遠離所有人類城市，理應是生態天堂，怎料島上佈滿信天翁的屍體 (包括大量幼鳥)，牠們的體內充滿人類的塑膠廢料，如樽蓋、膠管、打火機&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/132onXE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F132onXE.jpg&h=853341ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ST1o73f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FST1o73f.jpg&h=0050d386&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8XzdQc5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8XzdQc5.jpg&h=4edd8b67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1W7Z2R4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1W7Z2R4.jpg&h=dc1b1c6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wTE73eN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwTE73eN.jpg&h=139943ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"874aaca406e54dc536036915c5c7a310dc4d367c","tid":128193,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T15:21:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"374ea2e7972510bed38eb626807f658efdd8a16a","tid":128193,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T15:28:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbcf56da8ee9fcc5d307ca180b504d307298c374","tid":128193,"uid"